    dc:title "Two new species of Otiorhynchus Germar, 1822 of the subgenus Anchorrhynchus Reitter, 1914 from the Balkan Peninsula, with a key to species (Coleoptera Curculionidae: Entiminae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7334068>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7334062>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7334064> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7334068>
    dc:description "Figures 4 a–p. Male terminalia of Otiorhynchus species. Penis median lobe ventral, lateral view and median lobe apex of O. beieri: a, b, c; O. endroedii; d, e, f; O. maderi maderi; g, h, i; O roznerantii.i: j, k, l; Spiculum gastrale of O. pseudoschlaeflini: m; O. roznerantii: n. Tegmen of O. pseudoschlaeflini; o; O. roznerantii: p. Scale bar: 1 mm. Not to scale: c, f, i, l." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7334068/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7334062>
    dc:description "Figures 2 a–b. Habitus of Otiorhynchus species. O. schlaeflini: a, b male dorsal and lateral view. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7334062/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7334064>
    dc:description "Figures 3 a–r. Male terminalia of Otiorhynchus species. Penis median lobe ventral, lateral view and median lobe apex of O. schlaeflini: a, b, c; O. sabbadini; d, e, f; O. solariorum; g, h, i; O. bischoffianus: j, k, l; O. excellens: m, n, o; O. pseudochlaeflini: p, q, r. Scale bar: 1 mm. Not to scale: c, f, i, l, o, r." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7334064/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

